snippet.title: Cranky Cove trailer
snippet.description:
Cranky Cove is OUT NOW, only on the Playdate handheld system! Buy it or learn more at https://play.date/games/cranky-cove

Welcome to Cranky Cove, a stubborn little town in need of a guiding hand!

Use the crank to spin three rings, lining up workers, tools, and materials to craft items for the ever-demanding townsfolk.

From fresh-baked bread 🍞 to handcrafted jewelry 💍 and the treasures of the sea 🦀, every order helps the town grow.

With each new challenge, your customers demand more—can you keep up?


Credits:
Music: "8 Bit Onward" by HeatleyBros - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xbzOwijSj2Yn
